    <Statements>
      <Statement>Initiate and participate effectively in a range of collaborative discussions (one-on-one, in groups, and teacher-led) with diverse partners on grades 9&#8211;10 topics, texts, and issues, building on others&#8217; ideas and expressing their own clearly and persuasively.</Statement>
